title: Night Mode 6.1.0 - WordPress Plugin
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org Night Mode WordPress Plugin is the ideal solution to switch web page between Night Mode and normal style smoothly to improve the readability of text, images and videos. Night Mode WordPress Plugin Features Change Night Mode switch button style. Change Night Mode style background, text and links colors for webpage. One click to add in all your posts. One click to add in all your pages. Shortcode. Widget. Hide/show or toggle icon. Change position. Change title to any language. Image opacity. Image filter. Change Header and Footer background color. Show on home page – enable/disable Keep on with navigation – enable/disable
